snippet: The Michigan senior Sam Mikulak, who on Friday won the all-around title, earned a record-tying seventh individual N.C.A.A. gymnastics title with a victory on the parallel bars in Ann Arbor, Mich.
abstract: Michigan senior Sam Mikulak, earns a record-tying seventh individual NCAA gymnastics title with a victory on the parallel bars in Ann Arbor, Mich.
lead_paragraph: The Michigan senior Sam Mikulak, who on Friday won the all-around title, earned a record-tying seventh individual N.C.A.A. gymnastics title with a victory on the parallel bars in Ann Arbor, Mich.

headline.main: With Another Win, Mikulak Matches Record
